Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.95,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:こんな練習早くマスターするのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私はロボットじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:鮎原こずえは生きた人間だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:08.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:三日間で前後左右の空中回転をマスターせいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:09.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:絶対に何かの謀だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.71,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{NOTE:こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:14.80,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{NOTE:こずえちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ、なんなの、ママ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:23.06,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{NOTE:新しい体操のタイツを買ってきたわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:そこへ置いといて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.81,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.15,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{NOTE:じゃ、ここへ置きますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:44.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:昨日は練習に打ち込んだけどきっとこの特訓には理由があったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:49.37,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:入ったばかりの私に三日間で空中回転をマスターせよなんて…絶対に理由があるはずよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:50.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.38,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:中島先生に本当の事を聞こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:だって、私は体操ロボットじゃないんだもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.81,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{NOTE:—さ、準備はいいわね。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.98,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:前方空中に回転から始めるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:11.35,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:いいわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:前方空中に回転。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.69,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:今日中に…いいえ、午前中にいっぱいマスターしてみせるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.94,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:その時こそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:19.53,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:良い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:24.49,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:中島先生、出来ま—}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.68,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.97,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私、褒めてあげるからいらっしゃいと言った覚えはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:せ、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:51.52,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:一回ぐらい出来たからって完全とは言えないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.90,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:さ、今度は助走なしでやってごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:え？助走なし？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.98,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:出来るはずよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.23,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それとも怖いの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:でも、無茶です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:02.95,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:走る距離とスピードを徐々落として行けば必ずできるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.87,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:さ、何をぐずぐずしてるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.32,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:時間は待ってくれないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:10.12,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{NOTE:—先生、あなたし—\\N—何か言いたいことがあるなら休憩時間にしてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.71,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:約束の期限明日ですからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.75,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:たとえ詰まらない約束でも、約束は約束。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:やります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:助走なしできっとマスターします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.84,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:まず今までの半分の助走XXいいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.34,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:体を楽にして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:次から次に無理な注文がついてくる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:でも私は負けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:33.35,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:どんな陰謀だって必ずマスターして中島先生をXXXめてあげるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.56,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.23,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:約束は約束。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.40,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私だって約束を守ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.44,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:そのためにもくじけないで、この練習を早くマスターするのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.53,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:54.04,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。も一度。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:今度は助走なしでやります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.92,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.71,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:少しバランスが崩れもいくから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.96,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:やってごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:06.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.72,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:大丈夫です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.00,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:恐ろしいほどのファイトだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:41.13,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:三日間でマスターするために今日中にやり遂げようと言う気迫。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.76,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:もしや鮎原さんは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.22,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:何か感づいたなのでわ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:48.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:56.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私が本郷先生に侮辱されたことから、中島先生が私に駆虫回転をマスターさせると約束して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.85,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:しかも三日間で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:03.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:でも私が体操部で(XX・通用)することを証明するために(XXX・だいのうと)なの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:07.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:しかも、先生がかけの道具みたいに私をこんな特訓でしごくなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.45,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:そんな事がもし本当だったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:14.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私は中島先生を心から軽蔑するわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:マスターしたその瞬間に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.00,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.04,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:私を何とも思われてもいいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.17,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あなたは約束取りマスターしてさえくれれば。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.47,Alternative,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:でも、どうやら完全に近づいてるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:35.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:マスターしさ日がバレーの決勝戦の日では…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.68,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:もしか—}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:41.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:もしかしたらバレーの決勝戦に合わせての特訓。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.82,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:でも、まさか、そんな事。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.90,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.03,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.65,Default,Nakajima,0,0,0,,{NOTE:もう一息で完成よ。}
